      "writtenOn": "2017-09-20T06:45:06Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "it would be simpler to implement notification-encoding by following the example in https://godoc.org/go.chromium.org/gae/service/datastore#GetPLS\n\nfunc (s *Special) Load(props PropertyMap) error {\n  if foo, ok :\u003d props[\"foo\"]; ok \u0026\u0026 len(foo) \u003d\u003d 1 {\n    s.foo \u003d foo\n    delete(props, \"foo\")\n  }\n  return GetPLS(s).Load(props)\n}\n\nfunc (s *Special) Save(withMeta bool) (PropertyMap, error) {\n  props, err :\u003d GetPLS(s).Save(withMeta)\n  if err !\u003d nil {\n    return nil, err\n  }\n  props[\"foo\"] \u003d []Property{MkProperty(s.foo)}\n  return props, nil\n}",
      "revId": "1c2bab882815aaccc545de26c8873a962e918772",
